description: Performs FlowSOM (cluster n=15) and views the results with a heatmap and minimum spanning tree (MST). FlowSOM clusters are also visualized in a heatmap using MEM score. 2D plot with Flt-SNE and UMAP. Downsampling filter applied(1%).For use with FlowJo plugin uploaded data.
name: FlowJo Cluster Explorer - Quick View
